Tae-Gyeong.

110
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,160
I'm sorry.

111
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,240
Did you wait long?

112
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:37,879
Yes. Why were you so late?

113
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:39,680
I overslept.

114
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,959
You never oversleep.

115
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,240
