Is it okay?

131
00:09:11,450 --> 00:09:12,559
What about this one?

132
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,559
What about this?

133
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,210
How about this?

134
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,330
Are you broken?

135
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,330
You don't want to be my manager, do you?

136
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:01,879
I mean, no. It's not that.

137
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,090
Fine. I'm glad you're being honest.

138
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:08,120
Let's just look around here and go.

139
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:10,840
No. Let's look at everything.

140
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,210
I didn't even eat.

141
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:15,159
We agreed to eat together.

142
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,919
I wanted these.

143
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:43,799
Does it clash with our concept?

144
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,519
Why do you keep doing that?

145
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,559
What?

146
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,720
You keep glaring at me.

147
00:10:57,919 --> 00:10:59,559
And when I ask you something,

148
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,039
you just nod insincerely.

149
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,039
If you're going to do that,
just go home.

150
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,279
Are you mad?

151
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,799
Yes.

152
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,399
You came here to help me,

153
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,720
but you weren't helpful.

154
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,960
I'm sorry.

155
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:49,080
It's fine.

156
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:52,120
You must be tired
because you didn't get a lot of sleep.

157
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:56,159
You can go home after we drink this.

158
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,919
I'll just look around
some more by myself...

159
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,960
No!

160
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,799
I want to stay here...

161
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:10,559
with you.

162
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,159
I want to be here with you.

163
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:23,000
Oh, well...

164
00:12:24,759 --> 00:12:27,080
After seeing the clothes you chose,

165
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,799
I thought you'd need some help.

166
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:33,080
Oh, right. Fine.

167
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:51,840
Here.

168
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,799
Are these for me?

169
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:10,879
Yes.

170
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:15,639
I just wanted to get you a present.

171
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:20,679
Wear these
and don't be nervous on stage.

172
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,559
As for the clothes...

173
00:13:26,759 --> 00:13:28,399
You looked good in everything.

174
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,519
You have a small face,

175
00:13:32,399 --> 00:13:33,600
you're pale,

176
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,679
and you're handsome.

177
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,720
Oh, right. Well...

178
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,480
I need to buy a hat.

179
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,399
Can you help me choose one out?

180
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,919
Oh, my. It's cute.

181
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,919
It looks really cute.
I'll take a photo for you.

182
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,480
Hey.

183
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,120
Do you...

184
00:14:27,879 --> 00:14:29,200
want to take one with me?

185
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,759
Sure.

186
00:14:53,879 --> 00:14:55,159
(Slightly less handsome Tae-Gyeong)

187
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:58,399
(What do you think of this hat?
Noh Shin-Woo picked it out.)

188
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:01,039
I chose a great manager for him.

189
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,039
- What?
- What?

190
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:07,679
Oh, well...

191
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:14,480
Tae-Gyeong...

192
00:15:15,639 --> 00:15:17,879
is going to participate
in the New Light Prince Contest.

193
00:15:18,039 --> 00:15:19,639
I thought he'd struggle on his own,

194
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:21,440
so I had Shin-Woo
help him has his manager.

195
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:25,399
I see. Good job.

196
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:33,039
How are things between
you and Tae-Gyeong? Did you guys talk?

197
00:15:38,279 --> 00:15:40,360
- Not yet.
- Da-On!

198
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:43,519
- What?
- Don't look at me like that.

199
00:15:43,559 --> 00:15:46,720
You look really sad,
so it makes you look handsomer.

200
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,000
You make me laugh.

201
00:15:50,039 --> 00:15:52,639
Right. You should smile like that.

202
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:55,120
You're almost as handsome as me,

203
00:15:55,159 --> 00:15:57,840
so when you smile, you look quite nice.

204
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,679
So?

205
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,240
When are you going to talk to him?

206
00:16:05,639 --> 00:16:07,519
I want to talk to him in person,

207
00:16:08,519 --> 00:16:10,039
but we never bump into each other.

208
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,720
That makes sense.

209
00:16:12,919 --> 00:16:15,759
You can't come to the student council
room because of your exams,

210
00:16:15,799 --> 00:16:17,159
and you're in a different grade.

211
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:20,279
Shin-Woo and Tae-Gyeong
are always together,

212
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:23,480
so they fight
and make up really quickly.

213
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,559
Are you going to contact him?

214
00:16:32,879 --> 00:16:35,519
No. There's another way.

215
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:38,399
Right. You always know what to do.

216
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:42,000
I'll see you later, Namkung.

217
00:16:43,919 --> 00:16:45,360
Where are you going all of a sudden?

218
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,559
Something suddenly came up.
I'm really sorry.

219
00:17:09,799 --> 00:17:13,650
Gosh, we did a great job shopping today.

220
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,519
I'm going to win no matter what.

221
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,200
I'm sorry.

222
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,839
I sincerely want to apologize...

223
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:51,410
for what I did to you.

224
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,920
I was envious of you.

225
00:17:55,359 --> 00:17:58,759
I liked Da-On before you,

226
00:18:00,759 --> 00:18:02,890
but it seemed like Da-On...

227
00:18:03,079 --> 00:18:05,410
liked you more than me.

228
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:09,319
I thought that you were stealing
Da-On from me.

229
00:18:10,650 --> 00:18:12,720
Da-On doesn't even belong to me.

230
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:15,759
I...

231
00:18:16,319 --> 00:18:19,319
can't say that it's okay right now.

232
00:18:20,650 --> 00:18:22,680
But it will become okay.

233
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,680
We have something in common.

234
00:18:28,170 --> 00:18:30,599
We both really like Da-On.

235
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,119
I don't.

236
00:18:36,890 --> 00:18:40,170
Who does something like that
to someone they like?

237
00:18:43,799 --> 00:18:45,960
I have no right to like him.

238
00:18:46,410 --> 00:18:49,440
Do you remember what you said to me?

239
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:55,680
Hi. It's been three years
since I liked Sin Da-On.

240
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,170
My name is Lee So-Hee.

241
00:18:59,119 --> 00:19:01,960
When I met you, this is what I thought.

242
00:19:02,799 --> 00:19:06,599
"Gosh, she's so honest and cool."

243
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,480
That's when...

244
00:19:10,599 --> 00:19:12,480
I wanted to become friends with you.

245
00:19:13,799 --> 00:19:16,960
Out of all the people that I know,

246
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,240
you're the most courageous...

247
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,319
and coolest person.

248
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:28,240
So let's become friends one day, okay?

249
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,960
We could become friends from now on.

250
00:19:32,519 --> 00:19:34,279
To celebrate becoming friends...

251
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,480
Here.

252
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:42,240
What is this?

253
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:46,759
I heard you were participating
in the New Light Prince Contest.

254
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:49,410
Namkung told me.

255
00:19:50,410 --> 00:19:51,410
Right.

256
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:54,039
I got it because I thought
it would look good on you.

257
00:19:56,839 --> 00:19:59,319
Thank you, So-Hee.

258
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:02,319
Don't be.

259
00:20:03,119 --> 00:20:05,319
I'm more grateful, Tae-Gyeong.

260
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:12,359
I'll get going.

261
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:15,079
Okay. Goodbye.

262
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:17,480
Okay. I'll see you around.

263
00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:41,170
What are you thinking about?

264
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,519
Just...

265
00:20:44,359 --> 00:20:47,920
I wonder what Da-On is doing right now.

266
00:20:49,559 --> 00:20:52,359
So-Hee said it's been a while
since she saw Da-On too.

267
00:20:52,650 --> 00:20:54,240
He doesn't answer her calls either.

268
00:20:56,650 --> 00:20:58,079
Is he okay?

269
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:02,599
Do you miss him?

270
00:21:05,650 --> 00:21:06,839
I just...

271
00:21:09,359 --> 00:21:11,720
want to know if he's doing okay.

272
00:21:13,410 --> 00:21:14,599
I'm worried.

273
00:21:37,559 --> 00:21:39,359
I know you don't want to see me.

274
00:21:42,839 --> 00:21:45,410
But can you just give me
a moment of your time?

275
00:21:50,170 --> 00:21:52,279
After what happened between us,

276
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:56,960
I couldn't sleep,

277
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:00,839
and I couldn't eat.

278
00:22:04,079 --> 00:22:06,880
I thought I'd be more tormented
if I didn't say anything.

279
00:22:09,319 --> 00:22:11,680
I'm sorry for putting you through
all that pain...

280
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:13,839
just because I liked you.

281
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:17,680
I'm sorry for hurting
the person you like.

282
00:22:21,519 --> 00:22:25,279
You can stay mad at me if you want,
and it's okay if you hate me.

283
00:22:26,599 --> 00:22:27,720
But...

284
00:22:28,079 --> 00:22:31,160
I'm not okay with you saying
you never want to see me again.

285
00:22:41,039 --> 00:22:42,200
So-Hee.

286
00:22:43,119 --> 00:22:44,960
I understand, so stop crying.

287
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:47,079
Your eyes are going to get swollen.

288
00:22:51,119 --> 00:22:52,599
I don't hate you.

289
00:22:53,279 --> 00:22:55,480
I'll take back what I said about
never seeing you again.

290
00:22:56,279 --> 00:22:57,359
But...

291
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:02,200
I don't think we can
be good friends right now.

292
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,319
Right.

293
00:23:06,279 --> 00:23:07,960
I can wait.

294
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:13,119
Were you going somewhere?

295
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,799
To meet someone.

296
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,640
Is it Woo Tae-Gyeong?

297
00:23:25,839 --> 00:23:27,920
Tae-Gyeong is a good guy.

298
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,440
I can see why you like him now.

299
00:23:31,319 --> 00:23:32,359
Right.

300
00:23:32,839 --> 00:23:35,799
I know that Tae-Gyeong is a good guy.

301
00:23:36,799 --> 00:23:37,960
That's why...

302
00:23:41,279 --> 00:23:43,160
I'm going to start all over again.

303
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,960
You went through so much trouble
being my manager...

304
00:23:59,079 --> 00:24:01,160
and shopping with me.

305
00:24:03,079 --> 00:24:04,160
Thank you.

306
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:09,960
Thanks for the shoes too.

307
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,599
Hey, Tae-Gyeong.

308
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,000
Yes?

309
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,359
I'm sure you know this,

310
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:26,640
but I'm bad...

311
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,640
at expressing myself.

312
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:32,880
That's why when I met someone
as honest as you,

313
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:38,480
I thought it was interesting at first,
and I got curious,

314
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,960
and...

315
00:24:43,559 --> 00:24:45,960
I wanted to spend more time with you.

316
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,799
So?

317
00:24:53,839 --> 00:24:56,720
Right, so...

318
00:24:57,519 --> 00:24:59,279
What I want to say is...

319
00:25:06,519 --> 00:25:07,640
I...

320
00:25:09,279 --> 00:25:11,519
am not disqualified as your manager,
right?

321
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:17,759
Right. You'll continue to be my manager.

322
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:21,119
You have to stay by my side every day
and answer all of my questions...

323
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:23,359
and do everything I tell you to do.

324
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:24,799
Hey, that's...

325
00:25:24,839 --> 00:25:26,000
So...

326
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,960
don't worry and go home and sleep.

327
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:32,640
You didn't lose your job.

328
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:41,839
I had a lot of fun today.

329
00:25:43,319 --> 00:25:45,000
I'll see you at school.

330
00:26:04,559 --> 00:26:05,720
"Stay..."

331
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,000
"by my side."

332
00:26:14,359 --> 00:26:19,119
He knows
how to make a person's heart flutter.

333
00:26:45,079 --> 00:26:46,160
Hi,

334
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,359
Tae-Gyeong.

335
00:26:58,519 --> 00:27:02,039
=Light on Me=

336
00:27:02,599 --> 00:27:04,680
(How are things between you and Da-On?)

337
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,799
What do you think? Do we seem awkward?

338
00:27:06,839 --> 00:27:08,480
It's an hour before the contest.

339
00:27:08,519 --> 00:27:10,599
Where did it go? Where is it?

340
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:13,319
- Are you looking for something?
(- Did something happen?)

341
00:27:14,079 --> 00:27:15,160
(Tae-Gyeong.)

342
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,119
Shin-Woo...

343
00:27:30,039 --> 00:27:33,920
=Light on Me=

